title: Rain Luciano
text:
About Me
I am a Data Visualization Engineer with a specialization on Power BI. Using my proficiency in dashboard UI/UX design and Power BI best practices, I find fulfillment in bridging the gap between non-technical individuals and data. Let’s collaborate on transforming data into actionable insights and compelling stories.


Background
I graduated from Ateneo de Manila University in 2022 with a Bachelor’s and Master’s degree in Applied Mathematics Major in Mathematical Finance (AMF). I am currently a Data Visualization Engineer at LENA - Lately, Everything Needs Analytics.
